        pulmonology clinics
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with moderate and severe asthma on Symbicort SMART treatment

        Exclusion Criteria:

